label: Charleston Year Book, 1880
description: A report from the mayor, city council, and various governmental departments of Charleston, South Carolina for the year 1880.  The yearbook opens with an address from Mayor Courtenay followed by reports from various departments and an appendix recounting the history of Charleston.
